sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant UI as Wallet UI
  participant SVC as App Services
  participant DB as Local Encrypted DB

  User->>UI: Open app (offline)
  UI->>SVC: Request data
  SVC->>DB: Read local state
  DB-->>SVC: Data returned
  SVC-->>UI: Display data

  User->>UI: Create / Update record
  UI->>SVC: Write request
  SVC->>DB: Persist change locally
  DB-->>SVC: Stored
  SVC-->>UI: Operation successful
